    "title": "Adding a Cutscene to a Playground Book"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can use cutscenes to show animated explanations or introductions to concepts",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and scenarios. You place cutscenes alongside playground pages in a chapter.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-a-Subfolder-to-a-Chapter-Folder",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add a Subfolder to a Chapter Folder",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Add a cutscene by creating a new folder inside a chapter folder. The name of the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "subfolder must end with the suffix .cutscenepage. Cutscene folders require two parts:",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a manifest property list named ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Manifest.plist",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", and a PrivateResources folder that",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "contains the HTML content of the cutscene.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-Cutscene-Resources",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add Cutscene Resources",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Create cutscenes in Swift Playgrounds by using HTML and any resources that you reference",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in the HTML. The HTML you write for cutscenes can include CSS, JavaScript, and SVG",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for animations. Your cutscene can also include media such as images, sound, and video.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Place all of the resources used in a cutscene in its PrivateResources folder.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "To localize a cutscene, enclose the cutscene files in a localization",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "folder, such as en.lproj for English, inside the PrivateResources folder.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Important",
          "style": "important",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-the-Cutscene-Manifest",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add the Cutscene Manifest",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In Xcode, create a property list file called ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Manifest.plist",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " in the cutscene subfolder.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Choose ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "File > New > File",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", then choose the Property List template from ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "iOS > Resources",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Use the manifest property list to list a cutscene’s name and to reference the HTML",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "file that defines the cutscene.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The cutscene manifest property list has two keys:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "inlineContent": [
                          {
                            "text": "Required.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "strong"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " The path to the HTML file that contains the cutscene. The path is relative to the cutscene’s PrivateResources folder.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "code": "CutsceneReference",
                    "type": "codeVoice"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "inlineContent": [
                          {
                            "text": "Required.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "strong"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": " The name of the cutscene. Choose a name that will make sense to learners reading it in Swift Playgrounds.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "code": "Name",
                    "type": "codeVoice"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "type": "termList"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
